    "info": {
      "paragraphs": [
        "Jade Tiger drops the paylines entirely. Every left-to-right path through the reels is live - 243 of them - so a symbol only has to land somewhere on each reel to pay. Stack two tigers on one reel and every way through them counts twice.",
        "Wilds prowl the three inner reels and stand in for any symbol, so one wild-heavy screen can pay several symbols at once. They never appear on the first reel: a run has to be anchored by a real symbol.",
        "Land three Bamboo scatters to wake the free spins, where wilds run denser and the ways multiply fast. Power Bet raises every stake, and the Pick & Collect ritual banks jade credits until you hit the end tile."
      ],
